title: Food Distribution
description: Fresh produce, canned goods, dairy, bread, and pantry staples. Take what you need to feed your family.

title: Emergency Assistance
description: Facing an unexpected crisis? We provide immediate food assistance outside regular hours when possible.

title: USDA Commodities
description: We distribute USDA commodity foods through the Emergency Food Assistance Program (TEFAP).

title: Resource Referrals
description: Need additional help? We connect families with other community resources and assistance programs.
